These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-6-1::.
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cycling, biathlon, snowboarding, soccer, rugby, tennis, parkour
There are 7 different favourite colors: white, amber, orange, blood-red, yellow, pink, green
 1. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
 2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
 4. the person who likes green is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is cycling##5
 6. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who's sport is soccer##1
 7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 9. the person who likes amber is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person who likes blood-red is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is tennis##5
11. the person who's sport is tennis is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
12. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
13. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
14. the person who likes orange is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
15. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who likes yellow##5
16. the person who likes yellow is not the person who's sport is parkour##6
17. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who likes pink##3
18. the person who likes amber is not the person who's sport is snowboarding##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3     |    4    |   5    |   6    |     7      |
| Nationality   | cycling | soccer | rugby | tennis | parkour | snowboarding | biathlon |
| Pet           | blood-red   | pink    | green       | white     | orange    | yellow   | amber |

