12. the owner of the frog is in an even position##4
13. the indonesian is not the owner of the cat##6
14. the malaysian is between the indonesian and the owner of the hedgehog##2
15. the french is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
16. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the dog##1

